'''''Po di Sangui''''' ( '''Igiti cy'Amaraso''' ), ni  filimi [[Ubufaransa|y'amakinamico y'Abafaransa]][[Gineya-Biso|Bissau-Gineya yo mu]] 1996   iyobowe na Flora Gomes kandi yakozwe na Jean-Pierre Gallepe.<ref>https://www.trigon-film.org/en/movies/Po_di_sangui</ref> <ref name=":0">https://www.festival-cannes.com/en/films/po-di-sangui</ref>  Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Dulceneia Bidjanque mu mwanya wa mbere hamwe na Djuco Bodjan, Dadu Cissé, Adama Kouyaté na Edna Evora mu nshingano zabo.<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/films/tree-of-blood-po-di-sangui/</ref><ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/us/film593825.html</ref> 

Iyi filime yafashwe nkumugani nyafurika mumudugudu wamashyamba ya Amanha Lundju<ref>https://en.unifrance.org/movie/13750/po-di-sangui-l-arbre-aux-ames</ref>.  Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime.<ref name=":0" />

